@NODE "Icons" "Icons (dir)"

                                  @{fg shine}Icons (dir)@{fg text}

Most of the Icons are self explanatory and have the Tool (or Project) that they
were designed for as a name (but you may use them for whatever you like). I've
created a lot of AmigaGuide icons in the standard proposed by @{"Roman Patzner" LINK "Card"}.

With the exception of the Babe icon, I've stuck with the standard size and
format for the icons, so everything should be in order.

This archive contains the following icons:

